When we return to Rome again, we will most certainly stay at the Hotel Grifo.	We had a wonderful time and a lot of it is do to the great stay at Hotel Grifo.	We stayed at the Hotel Grifo during our two week trip to Italy for the first time!	On a trip to Rome five years ago we passed this lovely looking hotel and decided to stay there the next time, which we did in nov. 2008.	I would recommend this hotel to anyone, and will certainly stay here myself when I next return to Rome.	We had a nice four day stay at the hotel Grifo a few weeks ago.